&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+&amp;nbsp; years of adjusting claims at a senior level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Claims experience working in California is required. Experience in Arizona, Florida, Illinois, Pennsylvania, New Jersey or Georgia is preferred.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Licensing may be required in additional jurisdictions based on business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
